flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Start of production line cycle or receipt of new supplier parts.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Collect in-process quality data]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Monitoring - Analyze end-of-line audit results]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: RCA Service - Identify defects and countermeasures]
  N3 --> N4[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Monitor and improve FTT yield]
  N4 --> N5[Stream: STREAMS - Inspect supplier parts]
  N5 --> N6[Cortex: Remote Functions - Verify regulatory compliance]
  N6 --> N7{Decision: Determine quality checks, resource allocation, defect countermeasures, process improvements, supplier part inspections, and regulatory compliance actions.}
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced rework and scrap, improved first-pass yields, lowered warranty costs, enhanced OTIF performance.]
  N7 -->|High defect rate detected| B1[Trigger additional in-process checks]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Reduced rework and scrap]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N7 -->|Supplier part fails inspection| B2[Schedule rework]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Maintained CQA standards]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N7 -->|Non-compliance with regulations| B3[Initiate corrective actions]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Ensured regulatory compliance]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]